# data

**Instance Property**

The raw GeoJSON data.

## Declaration

```swift
get data(): D | undefined;
set data(data: D | undefined);
```

## Discussion

Use the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/ItemCollection/data] object to view the original GeoJSON data. To retrieve the data as MapKit JS items, use the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/ItemCollection/items] or [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/ItemCollection/getFlattenedItemList] objects.

## Item collection properties

- **getFlattenedItemList()**: A flattened array of items that includes annotations and overlays.
- **items**: A nested list of annotations, overlays, and other item collections.
